    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "what do you mean \"protect myself\"? it feels more like I'm just a coward who failed everyone. every time I think about trying to rebuild or talking to my wife, I just feel this crushing weight. like there's no actual way out of this mess, just more debt and more embarrassment. it feels like the only way to actually stop the noise in my head is to just... stop everything. does that even make sense?",
