    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"let go of the burden entirely\"... you're saying that it's okay to just not deal with it anymore? that there's some kind of peace in just... being done with all this? it's just that everything is so heavy, and the idea of a \"permanent end\" to the debt and the shame feels like the only thing that's actually certain.",
